description: Scientists carrying out a study for the Oswaldo Cruz Foundation tested 13 of the Brazilian sharpnose type shark taken from South Atlantic Ocean near Rio de Janeiro.
title: Not so Great White! Sharks high on COCAINE are marauding the seas around the Brazil coast after smugglers dump stash in the water

description: Running a new candidate less than 100 days before the election may be 'less than ideal' for Democrats, but they seem optimistic that replacing Joe Biden with VP Kamala Harris will fire up their base.
title: Democrats admit it's 'not ideal' for Kamala Harris who has some 'challenges' to launch presidential campaign with just 105 days to the election but insist she could solve their voter 'enthusiasm' problem to beat Trump

description: Kayden Ely, 11, resorted to holding up a tear-jerking sign by the railroad tracks of his small Georgia town after his mother's abrupt death.
title: Georgia boy, 11, is forced to stand next to railroad tracks with heartbreakingly humiliating sign after his mother's sudden death

description: Bring it on!' is the response from Republicans to the almost certain prospect that Kamala Harris is to be their opponent in November.
title: Kamala Harris needs to be installed as President now so she can fight Donald Trump as an equal, writes JUSTIN WEBB

description: Education about online safety can help prevent deaths like that of a teen who fell victim to a sextortion scam, a coroner says.
title: Heartbreaking seven-word note found after Australian teen took his own life

description: A magnitude 6.1 earthquake struck a close Australian neighbour on Monday.
title: Magnitude 6.1 earthquake strikes Vanuatu

description: Police recorded more than a million crimes against women and girls in 2022/23 - accounting for almost a fifth of all offences excluding fraud - as experts say we are in a 'national emergency'.
title: Violence against women and girls is a 'national emergency', police chief warns - as almost 3,000 crimes recorded every day
